profile:
Over the past 12 years we have been providing affordable services for people that need assistance with jobs around the house or the office. We provide more than 20 different services and have expertise in all areas that we promote our business.  
 
We have a very strong belief that customer service needs to come first and our honest approach from the time you call until the time the job is completed will be refreshing.  We are happy to give suggestions, complete already started jobs or take on a large project with complete confidence.  Contact us today and let's get something done!

Full Service Contracting
Whether you're looking to update your kitchen or want to embark on a new build, let Three Point Contracting make your vision come to life. With years of experience in both the commercial and residential construction, Three Point Contracting has the knowledge, connections, and dedication to quality that you and your home deserve. With past projects in Collingwood, Muskoka, and Waterloo we are currently focusing on new builds and renovations in Stratford and surrounding areas.

profile:
As the owner of DZ Carpentry, my philsophy is simple: listen to what people want and assist them in making their home construction or renovation dreams come true.

Understanding what people want, and working with them to achieve their goals is what sets me apart. I won't tell you what to do, but I will offer you alternatives and allow you, the customer, to make the final decision that works best for you.

It is my attention to detail that differentiates me. I believe in quality over quantity and in doing the job right the first time.
